Subject: Cannot Change Current Password Even when Entering the Correct Current Password
Description: When I log on, I am prompted to change my current password. However, when I enter my current password, an error message in red states, "The password provided is different from the existing password" even though I copied and pasted the current password. (This stopped me from logging on to our test server, so the information I provided about platform, server ID, etc. is taken from our production server).
